javamoon.construct.source
Class CollectorType

java.lang.Object
  javamoon.construct.source.CollectorAbstract
      javamoon.construct.source.CollectorType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Collector
public class CollectorType
extends CollectorAbstract

First phase of the parsing. It collects the namespace and types of the system. At the end of this process we have the following elements: namespaces (packages) classes types comments imports

Version:
1.0
Author:
Raúl Marticorena

reset

public void reset()
Resets the state of the collector. It sets up the package as anonymous and removes the name of the current file. It also removes the current imports and comments. The reason is to begin the new phase without a package and file pre-established.
